The Lord Jesus,
on the night before he was handed over,
took bread, and,
giving thanks,
broke it and said:
"Take [this] and eat,
this is my body
which is handed over for you."
{{Translator|Edward Tambling}}}}

{{mdl|4}}{{Translation|German|
Der Herr Jesus nahm
in der Nacht, in der er verraten wurde,
