==General Information==
{{Title|''O quantus luctus''}}
{{Composer|Giovanni Pierluigi da Palestrina}}

{{Voicing|4|ATTB}}
{{Genre|Sacred|Motets|Antiphons}} for Lauds of {{Cat|St. Martin}}
{{Language|Latin}}
{{Instruments|A cappella}}
